      "pos_sentences": [
        {
          "text": "My friends and college life as being a hosteller enjoyed my hostel Life thats the best part",
          "name": "Genga K",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Sc + M.Sc"
        },
        {
          "text": "As for as college attending events and shouting our lungs out culturals",
          "name": "Genga K",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Sc + M.Sc"
        },
        {
          "text": "Campus life, course outcome, placement are the things that i liked in my college",
          "name": "Dharshini R",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Sc + M.Sc"
        },
        {
          "text": "Course outcome. Placment,faculty are the thungs i like about my college",
          "name": "Dharshini R",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Sc + M.Sc"
        },
        {
          "text": "Internships provided is mainly the best feature of this course that is available",
          "name": "Dharshini R",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Sc + M.Sc"
        },
        {
          "text": "Melina is the department function of the Msc which will be fun and entertaining",
          "name": "Pooja M",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Sc + M.Sc"
        },
        {
          "text": "I like most of the club events like hackathons,code quiz",
          "name": "Pooja M",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Sc + M.Sc"
        },
        {
          "text": "The library facilities in the CIT was good.",
          "name": "Sanjay A",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Sc + M.Sc"
        },
        {
          "text": "Hostel life is good. College surrounding is more than good with peaceful environment. Staffs are friendly except some of the staffs. There is no oressure in examination like other departments which is rare.",
          "name": "yazhini karthik",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Sc + M.Sc"
        },
        {
          "text": "In my college we have good placement opportunities.",
          "name": "Sneghaa",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Sc + M.Sc"
        }
      ],
      "neg_sentences": [
        {
          "text": "Placement is not 100 percent anymore in this college",
          "name": "Dharshini R",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Sc + M.Sc"
        },
        {
          "text": "Tution fees is bit more expensive and I feel like management is not taking care of the needs of the students.",
          "name": "yazhini karthik",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Sc + M.Sc"
        },
        {
          "text": "After internships, staffs mostly prefer us to self study rather than teaching.",
          "name": "Sruthi",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Sc + M.Sc"
        },
        {
          "text": "We were asked to pay semester fees even during our internships.",
          "name": "Sruthi",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Sc + M.Sc"
        },
        {
          "text": "The campus environment and infrastructure can be upgraded. It gives better feel for both students and the faculty",
          "name": "Sruthi",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Sc + M.Sc"
        },
        {
          "text": "Course structure is poor and fee is too high for these structures",
          "name": "Vishnu",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Sc + M.Sc"
        },
        {
          "text": "Staff are not equipped with latest technologies",
          "name": "Vishnu",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Sc + M.Sc"
        },
        {
          "text": "Forcing the students to make thesis on irrelevant topics",
          "name": "Vishnu",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Sc + M.Sc"
        },
        {
          "text": "Hostel gate timings became very strict in recent days (8 pm) which is very uncomfortable for us.",
